snippet.title: TEXNOPLAZM Reveal Trailer || Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
Entroducing TEXNOPLAZM, a First person brawler/shooter spinoff of 
Ghostware with a completely new cast of characters.
Defeat enemies with their own weapons, switch between three combat styles during fights, blend movement and combat abilities for inventive takedowns.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2527710/TEXNOPLAZM/

pronounced "Technoplasm"
